text: int main ( ) { int a , b , i , gcd , lcm ; int T ; scanf ( "%d" , & T ) ; while ( T -- ) { scanf ( "%d %d" , & a , & b ) ; for ( i = 1 ; i <= a && i <= b ; i ++ ) { if ( a % i == 0 && b % i == 0 ) { gcd = i ; } } lcm = ( a * b ) / gcd ; printf ( "%d %d" , gcd , lcm ) ; } return 0 ; }
